  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd4 \u0dba\u0dd4\u0daf \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc4\u0dd4\u0daf\u0da7 \u0d85\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d87\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An American warship has entered the China Sea without permission",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "China's People's Liberation Army emphasizes that the United States destroyer USS Benfold was sailing off the Xisha Islands in the South China Sea without the Chinese government's permission, and that Chinese security forces had observed it and issued warnings.",
        "The US military's actions violated China's sovereignty and security interests, undermined peace and stability in the South China Sea, and violated international law and norms governing international relations, Tian Junli, spokesman for the Chinese People's Liberation Army's Southern Command, said in a statement.",
        "\"The facts have proven once again that the United States is in every sense a security risk-maker in the South China Sea and a destroyer of regional peace and stability,\" Tian said.",
        "He said the Chinese military command is always alert to protect national sovereignty and security and peace and stability in the South China Sea."
      ],
